[[User:Kiltpin|Kiltpin]] ([[User talk:Kiltpin|talk]]) 00:16, 16 December 2011 (UTC) :Fixed. —[[User:Ed!|'''Ed!''']][[User talk:Ed!|'''(talk)''']] 00:55, 16 December 2011 (UTC) == Math problem == "Over the course of four days and four missions, he downed five Soviet aircraft;[5] two on 21 January and one each on 22 and 23 January.[4]" 2+1+1=4, not 5. — Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[Special:Contributions/98.231.236.158|98.231.236.158]] ([[User talk:98.231.236.158|talk]]) 05:10, 16 December 2011 (UTC) :The following sentences establish the fifth kill. —[[User:Ed!|'''Ed!''']][[User talk:Ed!|'''(talk)''']] 21:55, 17 December 2011 (UTC) == be careful == We have to be careful that we are neutral and don't side with this dead guy but give equal weight to the story of the USAF. — Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[User:Eclipse ahead cover your ears|Eclipse ahead cover your ears]] ([[User talk:Eclipse ahead cover your ears|talk]] • [[Special:Contributions/Eclipse ahead cover your ears|contribs]]) 03:55, 21 March 2015 (UTC)
